divs: Sighting Detailsi was looking at raw images taken Jun 07 2012 (SCET), Titan (T-84) Flyby, 959 km (596 mi) taken from the Cassini Spacecraft orbiting Saturn. I found this UFO that looks way to familiar to me because i seen something similar to the object in the picture its top looks like a triangle craft with a long tail behind the UFO. the picture is a raw image from NASA's Cassini Spacecraft and i dont own any of these pictures there owned by NASA.
Summary: Picture from Titan (T-84) Flyby raw image shows ufo
